      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nFound this old patch on b2_4 without any reviewers, and I don't see anything similar for master, so it doesn't appear to be a backported patch.\n\nIt does seem like a useful cleanup from reading the description in LU-30 (which would be nice to have in the commit comment here also), so it might be worthwhile to update this to master?",
